data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite single-story home with a 2-car garage, nestled in Breathtaking PebbleCreek neighborhood.  As you step inside you are captivated by the breathtaking interior. From the cathedral entry to the high vaulted ceilings that create a sense of grandeur. Tile floors grace every inch of the space. The heart of this home is the stunning eat-in kitchen, a culinary masterpiece. White cabinetry, almost new top-end LG stainless steel appliances, a Viking cooktop, and under/over cabinet lighting define this space. The full tile backsplash, breakfast bar, stylish counters, and pantry add both functionality and style to this gourmet haven. The large primary bedroom with sitting area, spacious  en suite bathroom with custom  shower, and enormous walk in closet Natural light flows through the 3-panel arcadia sliding doors.The immaculate backyard has a stunning Pebble finish solar-heated pool w/waterfall to enjoy & lots of patio space. Enjoy lower energy bills with the Owned Solar Panels, Pelican whole house filtration system ensures the highest quality water throughout, while a hot water circulation pump adds convenience to your daily life. This residence is not just a home; it's a showcase of thoughtful design and meticulous care. Live in luxury and comfort, surrounded by elegance at every turn. Your dream home awaits, complete with modern conveniences and timeless charm.
And one can't forget about the amazing Community facilities including 3 outdoor pools, one indoor pool,work out facilities, fitness classes, community art center, bocce ball, walking paths, parks, restaurants, tennis, pickleball, 3 world class golf courses.
